Package com.intellij.ide.actions

Class OpenProjectFileChooserDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.openapi.fileChooser.FileChooserDescriptor
      • com.intellij.ide.actions.OpenProjectFileChooserDescriptor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class OpenProjectFileChooserDescriptor
extends FileChooserDescriptor
    Intended for use in actions related to opening or importing existing projects. Due to a high I/O impact SHOULD NOT be used in any other cases.
